    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grinding Guilds mixes Auto Battler and ARPG elements with Active and Idle modes. Pick your hero, level up and upgrade abilities. Hire allies for your guild, get loot and equip Pacts to create unique builds. Find the best strategy to defeat all bosses and reclaim all regions.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Active and Auto mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of your hero and lead your guild to victory, or sit back and watch them battle hordes of enemies as an Idle RPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/daab35ea8329d9e2d80e7cb5e9abc5b4.poster.avif?t=1766672330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/daab35ea8329d9e2d80e7cb5e9abc5b4.webm?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/daab35ea8329d9e2d80e7cb5e9abc5b4.mp4?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Assemble your guild</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dozens of allies with unique abilities to choose from and create your party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/1dd86ecb67891f989fadc9b05a0be071.avif?t=1766672330\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equip your units</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each unit can be equipped with up to 6 items that greatly modify their stats. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/b36b166364f90c45e8b0fdfa06b063dd.poster.avif?t=1766672330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/b36b166364f90c45e8b0fdfa06b063dd.webm?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/b36b166364f90c45e8b0fdfa06b063dd.mp4?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skill trees</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your abilities and customize them. Each ability has its own skill tree with multiple upgrades for you to create amazing builds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/c06fa3ae7cc82302fcd16918f4775f26.poster.avif?t=1766672330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/c06fa3ae7cc82302fcd16918f4775f26.webm?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/c06fa3ae7cc82302fcd16918f4775f26.mp4?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find the best strategy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position your units and equip Pacts to provide bonuses to your heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/288314fe56cc759443cd2efb53c6019e.poster.avif?t=1766672330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/288314fe56cc759443cd2efb53c6019e.webm?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/288314fe56cc759443cd2efb53c6019e.mp4?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your battles, defeating a boss region will unlock new crafting recipes and new allies. Grind your way against increasingly harder enemies, defeat all bosses and reclaim all regions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/79c6c331ed1815340bc3d26ef8c4ee0e.poster.avif?t=1766672330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/79c6c331ed1815340bc3d26ef8c4ee0e.webm?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299780/extras/79c6c331ed1815340bc3d26ef8c4ee0e.mp4?t=1766672330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
